name: the soul of music
description:
found a sample a few months back that i reversed and chopped it to make this loop that was so beautiful I didn't think it needed anything else on top of it. the photo is created with nightcafe studio's text to art AI function. I gave the AI the prompt "the soul of music" 

made for OBJKT4OBJKT, unbelievably happy to join this community for the 2nd time. enjoy the art!
